    "description": {
      "chat": "",
      "gmnotes": "",
      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>Soul surge was innovated by Hanakan mystics concomitant with the attunement of their soulstones. With this spell, you draw forth a tiny bit of your essence to attack your opponent, losing a number of Hit Points equal to the number of damage dice you roll for your soul surge. Attempt a ranged attack against a single target&rsquo;s EAC, adding your key ability score modifier to the attack roll instead of your Dexterity modifier if it&rsquo;s higher. Your soul surge does piercing damage that has the force descriptor, and the amount of damage it does depends on the level at which it&rsquo;s cast.</p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>1st</strong>: </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">When you cast </span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">soul surge </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">as a 1st-level spell, it deals 3d8 damage to the target.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>2nd</strong>: </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">When you cast </span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">soul surge </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">as a 2nd-level spell, it deals 6d8 damage to the target.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>3rd</strong>: </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">When you cast </span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">soul surge </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">as a 3rd-level spell, it deals 10d8 damage to the target.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>4th</strong>: </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">When you cast </span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">soul surge </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">as a 4th-level spell, it deals 14d8 damage to the target.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>5th</strong>: </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">When you cast </span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">soul surge </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">as a 5th-level spell, it deals 21d8 damage to the target.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>6th</strong>: </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">When you cast </span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">soul surge </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">as a 6th-level spell, it deals 24d8 damage to the target.</span> </p>"
    },
